# Canonical .gitignore for Defra Node services.
#
# Notes:
#   - `.vscode/*` is ignored EXCEPT launch.json and tasks.json, which are committed
#     so the whole team shares the same run/debug config. (settings.json is ignored
#     here; some repos commit it instead to pin the SonarLint project key — see below.)
#   - `.public` is the Vite build output; keep it ONLY for repos that build client
#     assets. Remove the line for API-only repos.
#   - `.sonarlint/` must be ignored (SonarLint connected-mode cache, machine-local).
#   - `keys/` only applies to services that generate/persist local auth keys
#     (e.g. the Defra ID stub). Omit it otherwise.
.DS_Store
.npm/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
.idea
.public
node_modules
npm-debug.log
coverage
.cache
.eslintcache
.envrc
tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
.env
.sonarlint/

# Auth-key services only (e.g. Defra ID stub) — omit if not applicable:
# keys/
